<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About - Cooking</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('./partials/main-header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="about-content">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <p>
                    Welcome to our Cooking website! We share delicious recipes, cooking
                    tips, and culinary inspiration to help you enjoy cooking at home.
                </p>

                <!-- Cooking Image -->
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="/image/cooking.jpg" alt="Cooking Image" />
                </div>

                <h2>Why We Love Cooking</h2>
                <p>
                    Cooking is an art form and a way to connect with others. It’s about
                    bringing people together around the table, creating new flavors, and
                    sharing memories. Whether you’re a beginner or an experienced chef,
                    there’s always something new to learn.
                </p>

                <button id="more-info-btn" onclick="document.location.href='/login'">Get Started</button>
                <div id="more-info" class="hidden">
                    <p>
                        Join our cooking community! Share your own recipes, get inspired by
                        others, and learn tips and tricks from expert chefs. Cooking is more
                        than just a hobby; it’s a way to express creativity and explore new
                        cultures.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Additional Features Section -->
                <section class="cooking-features">
                    <h2>Our Features</h2>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <img src="/image/delicious.jpg" alt="Feature 1" />
                        <h3>Delicious Recipes</h3>
                        <p>
                            Find a variety of recipes for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and
                            desserts to suit all tastes and skill levels.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <img src="/image/sheff.png" alt="Feature 2" />
                        <h3>Cooking Tips</h3>
                        <p>
                            Get expert tips to improve your cooking techniques, whether you're
                            boiling, baking, or grilling.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <img src="/image/community.jpg" alt="Feature 3" />
                        <h3>Community Sharing</h3>
                        <p>
                            Share your own recipes and ideas with a passionate community of
                            cooking enthusiasts.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </section>
        </main>

        <%- include('./partials/main-footer') %>